high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the sofa.
Take the cookie from the sofa.
Turn around move towards the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Take the cookie from the sofa and turn on the floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and turn left move towards the sofa.
Pick the cookie from the sofa.
Turn right and turn left move towards the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a cookie by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the sofa.
Pick up cookie from the sofa.
After turning around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Shifting cookie from one place to another.
